OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy morning with a few
OL,6,Fshowers. Becoming drier by the
OL,7,Fafternoon with long sunny spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping. A little breezy in the
OL,9,Fmorning but winds soon becoming light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry evening with late sunny
OL,12,Fthen clear spells. Turning cloudier
OL,13,Ffrom the south overnight with heavy
OL,14,Frain reaching Orkney by dawn.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FCloudy with heavy rain
OL,17,Fspreading northeast. Orkney turns dry
OL,18,Fthrough the afternoon, but rain
OL,19,Fcontinues in Shetland. Strong winds
OL,20,Ffor Orkney but gales or possibly
OL,21,Fsevere gales for Shetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
