OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBright
OL,6,For sunny spells with showers on Sunday
OL,7,Fand Monday. Mostly dry with sunny
OL,8,Fspells on Tuesday. Strong winds and
OL,9,Frisk of gales Sunday, then winds
OL,10,Fbecoming light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
